    <unit id="overviewStats">
      <segment>
        <source> 23+ event kinds · 7 entry points · 379 green specs · zero Angular imports in <pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">core</pc> · Apache-2.0 </source>
        <target> 23+ Ereignistypen · 7 Einstiegspunkte · 379 bestandene Specs · keine Angular-Imports in <pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">core</pc> · Apache-2.0 </target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="eventKindsTitle">
      <segment>
        <source><pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_SPAN" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_SPAN" type="other" dispStart="&lt;span class=&quot;card__dot card__dot--orange&quot;&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/span&gt;"></pc>Event kinds </source>
        <target><pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_SPAN" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_SPAN" type="other" dispStart="&lt;span class=&quot;card__dot card__dot--orange&quot;&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/span&gt;"></pc>Ereignistypen </target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="eventKindsBody">
      <segment>
        <source> One append-only <pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">ConversationEvent</pc> union covers messages, tool bursts, waits, and orchestrator decisions. Unknown kinds render as fallback rows. </source>
        <target> Ein append-only <pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">ConversationEvent</pc>-Union-Typ deckt Nachrichten, Tool-Blöcke, Wartezeiten und Orchestrator-Entscheidungen ab. Unbekannte Typen erscheinen als Fallback-Zeilen. </target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="coreTitle">
      <segment>
        <source><pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_SPAN" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_SPAN" type="other" dispStart="&lt;span class=&quot;card__dot card__dot--blue&quot;&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/span&gt;"></pc>Framework-free core </source>
        <target><pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_SPAN" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_SPAN" type="other" dispStart="&lt;span class=&quot;card__dot card__dot--blue&quot;&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/span&gt;"></pc>Framework-unabhängiger Kern </target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="coreBody">
      <segment>
        <source><pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">coding-agent-chat/core</pc> is plain TypeScript: the <pc id="1" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">ConversationEvent</pc> contract plus <pc id="2" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">projectConversation()</pc>. Backends, SSR code and tests can import it without Angular. </source>
        <target><pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">coding-agent-chat/core</pc> ist reines TypeScript: der <pc id="1" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">ConversationEvent</pc>-Vertrag plus <pc id="2" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">projectConversation()</pc>. Backends, SSR-Code und Tests können es ohne Angular importieren. </target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="entryPointsTitle">
      <segment>
        <source><pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_SPAN" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_SPAN" type="other" dispStart="&lt;span class=&quot;card__dot card__dot--purple&quot;&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/span&gt;"></pc>Entry points </source>
        <target><pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_SPAN" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_SPAN" type="other" dispStart="&lt;span class=&quot;card__dot card__dot--purple&quot;&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/span&gt;"></pc>Einstiegspunkte </target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="entryPointsBody">
      <segment>
        <source> Seven import paths keep optional features separate. <pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">core</pc> is plain TypeScript with no Angular dependency. <pc id="1" equivStart="START_LINK" equivEnd="CLOSE_LINK" type="link" dispStart="&lt;a href=&quot;#entry-points&quot;&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/a&gt;">View samples</pc>. </source>
        <target> Sieben Importpfade halten optionale Funktionen getrennt. <pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">core</pc> ist reines TypeScript ohne Angular-Abhängigkeit. <pc id="1" equivStart="START_LINK" equivEnd="CLOSE_LINK" type="link" dispStart="&lt;a href=&quot;#entry-points&quot;&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/a&gt;">Beispiele ansehen</pc>. </target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="integrationPointsTitle">
      <segment>
        <source><pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_SPAN" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_SPAN" type="other" dispStart="&lt;span class=&quot;card__dot card__dot--green&quot;&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/span&gt;"></pc>Host integration points </source>
        <target><pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_SPAN" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_SPAN" type="other" dispStart="&lt;span class=&quot;card__dot card__dot--green&quot;&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/span&gt;"></pc>Host-Integrationen </target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="integrationPointsBody">
      <segment>
        <source> Four injection tokens have safe defaults. Provide <pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">CHAT_MEDIA_LIGHTBOX</pc> to enable image enlargement. <pc id="1" equivStart="START_LINK" equivEnd="CLOSE_LINK" type="link" dispStart="&lt;a href=&quot;#rendering&quot;&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/a&gt;">See the rendering demo</pc>. </source>
        <target> Vier Injection Tokens haben Standardwerte. Stelle <pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">CHAT_MEDIA_LIGHTBOX</pc> bereit, um Bilder vergrößerbar zu machen. <pc id="1" equivStart="START_LINK" equivEnd="CLOSE_LINK" type="link" dispStart="&lt;a href=&quot;#rendering&quot;&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/a&gt;">Darstellungsdemo ansehen</pc>. </target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="themeCardTitle">
      <segment>
        <source><pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_SPAN" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_SPAN" type="other" dispStart="&lt;span class=&quot;card__dot card__dot--orange&quot;&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/span&gt;"></pc>Theme</source>
        <target><pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_SPAN" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_SPAN" type="other" dispStart="&lt;span class=&quot;card__dot card__dot--orange&quot;&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/span&gt;"></pc>Theme</target>
