    <unit id="themeCardBody">
      <segment>
        <source> Import the optional stylesheet for the default theme. Set <pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">data-studio-theme=&quot;light&quot;</pc> on any parent for the light palette. </source>
        <target> Importiere das optionale Stylesheet für das Standard-Theme. Setze <pc id="0" equivStart="START_TAG_CODE" equivEnd="CLOSE_TAG_CODE" type="other" dispStart="&lt;code&gt;" dispEnd="&lt;/code&gt;">data-studio-theme=&quot;light&quot;</pc> auf einem beliebigen Elternelement für die helle Palette. </target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
